狀。\r\n                           書記官  張嫚凌\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　8 　　月　　2 　　日","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SLDM/111%2c%e6%af%92%e8%81%b2%2c360%2c20220729%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SLDM,111,毒聲,360,20220729,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"毒聲","JNO":"360","JDATE":"20220729","JTITLE":"聲請觀察勒戒"}